(A) go to website : https://in.search.yahoo.com/search?fr=mcafee&type=E210IN826G0&p=hub+dockerhub.com

(1) how to download images : sudo docker pull mysql
(2) check images : docker images 
(3) history with image : docker history (imageID)
(3) how to container Id : docker create (ImageID)
(4) docker check container : docker ps - a
(5) docker run command : docker run -d --name israyal  mysql     [ditached mode d means]
(6) docker inspect to changes container the file system : docker diff (containerId)
(7) docker start container : docker start (containerID)
(8) running state container check it : docker ps 
(9) docker container login : docker exec -it (containerID) /bin/bash  	[container is a login now container data is there]
(10) login the container create file : touch newfile.txt
(11) add information : echo "this file login to the container" >> newfile.txt
(12) check the information : cat newfile.txt			[exit]
(13) check the all information : ls -ltr
(14) docker details of the tomcat : docker inspect MySQL
(15) docker inspect to changes container the file system : docker diff (containerId)
(16) unresponding container CMD : docker kill (containerID)   			[kill cmd forcefully shutdown for the contaner]  
(17) container stop : docker stop (containerID)					[it means gracefully shotdown for the container]
(18) remove container : docker rm (containerID)
(19) remove image : docker rmi (mysql)
(20) remove all containers at one time : docker rm $(docker ps -a -q)
(21) docker image build : docker build -t MySQL .

